1
00:00:12,784 --> 00:00:13,685
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Please!</i></font>

2
00:00:15,187 --> 00:00:17,055
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't. Sorry.</font>

3
00:00:20,959 --> 00:00:23,095
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, what do you want to eat for dinner?</font>

4
00:00:26,798 --> 00:00:28,133
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stewed hamburger steak.</font>

5
00:00:29,368 --> 00:00:30,369
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

6
00:00:30,602 --> 00:00:31,670
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please!</font>

7
00:00:31,770 --> 00:00:34,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. That's never happening.</font>

8
00:00:34,706 --> 00:00:37,075
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that Abe?</font>

9
00:00:38,410 --> 00:00:40,946
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He must be asking girls out again.
He never gives up.</font>

10
00:00:41,346 --> 00:00:43,181
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It looks that way.</font>

11
00:00:48,086 --> 00:00:51,056
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What if he tries to ask me out again?</font>

12
00:00:51,356 --> 00:00:52,958
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not likely.</font>

13
00:01:00,966 --> 00:01:02,534
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please help me!</font>

14
00:01:02,601 --> 00:01:04,870
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm in a desperate situation.</font>

15
00:01:06,738 --> 00:01:10,909
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Drama Workshop Newcomer Production
<i>Sleeping Beauty."</i></font>

16
00:01:11,376 --> 00:01:13,178
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe, you joined a drama club?</font>

17
00:01:13,278 --> 00:01:14,279
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

18
00:01:16,915 --> 00:01:18,483
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Writer and director, Jun Abe"?</font>

19
00:01:20,285 --> 00:01:23,655
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I guess I sort of
have a talent for it.</font>

20
00:01:23,755 --> 00:01:24,990
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm participating in it.</font>

21
00:01:25,924 --> 00:01:28,794
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">As always, you have no self-awareness.</font>

22
00:01:29,027 --> 00:01:31,530
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it's supposed to open soon,</font>

23
00:01:31,797 --> 00:01:35,167
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but the prince and princess
both got hit with high fevers.</font>

24
00:01:38,303 --> 00:01:39,137
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What will you do?</font>

25
00:01:39,771 --> 00:01:40,739
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please!</font>

26
00:01:41,373 --> 00:01:43,041
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want you to take the role!</font>

27
00:01:45,744 --> 00:01:48,947
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I've never acted before,</font>

28
00:01:49,047 --> 00:01:50,482
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Please, Uehara!
-and I'm just not...</font>

29
00:01:55,887 --> 00:01:57,255
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

30
00:01:57,355 --> 00:01:59,157
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, I'm begging you.</font>

31
00:02:01,126 --> 00:02:02,160
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

32
00:02:07,132 --> 00:02:09,835
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara was the only person
I could see as the prince.</font>

33
00:02:12,971 --> 00:02:14,806
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everyone just wants Uehara.</font>

34
00:02:25,183 --> 00:02:26,051
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How lovely!</font>

35
00:02:26,885 --> 00:02:27,886
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you get it, Yoshikawa?</font>

36
00:02:27,953 --> 00:02:29,688
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If Uehara did this, it would be so cool!</font>

37
00:02:29,755 --> 00:02:30,655
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right?</font>

38
00:02:30,722 --> 00:02:33,425
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait. If Uehara is the prince,</font>

39
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,427
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">the princess has to be...</font>

40
00:02:41,099 --> 00:02:42,033
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Yes!</font>

41
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:43,668
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">On that day,</font>

42
00:02:43,769 --> 00:02:47,973
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">enveloped by warm sunlight filtering
through the trees,</font>

43
00:02:51,643 --> 00:02:55,180
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">in that place where the violets
were in full bloom...</font>

44
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:58,316
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It feels like fate</font>

45
00:02:58,416 --> 00:03:01,686
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that I met you there."</font>

46
00:03:02,721 --> 00:03:05,323
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're next! Go ahead, Uehara.</font>

47
00:03:05,423 --> 00:03:06,825
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you, I'm not doing it.</font>

48
00:03:07,726 --> 00:03:09,027
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I can't see the TV.</font>

49
00:03:11,763 --> 00:03:14,399
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You could at least help a little.</font>

50
00:03:14,966 --> 00:03:16,701
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And Abe needs help.</font>

51
00:03:17,803 --> 00:03:20,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to bed, so go on home.</font>

52
00:03:22,007 --> 00:03:22,874
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay!</font>

53
00:03:22,974 --> 00:03:24,576
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay! I'm sorry!</font>

54
00:03:24,676 --> 00:03:25,510
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The prince's line...</font>

55
00:03:25,610 --> 00:03:28,380
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Don't make that sad face,
and please smile for me.</font>

56
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,749
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I swear..."</font>

57
00:03:31,116 --> 00:03:32,517
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Say that line, Uehara.</font>

58
00:03:32,617 --> 00:03:34,586
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I swear..."</font>

59
00:03:34,653 --> 00:03:35,520
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Night.</font>

60
00:03:35,587 --> 00:03:37,622
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I swear..."</font>

61
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:43,495
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I swear eternal love to
that smile of yours."</font>

62
00:03:44,629 --> 00:03:46,398
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">As if I would ever say that line.</font>

63
00:03:48,934 --> 00:03:52,804
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was my one chance to
hear him swear eternal love to me.</font>

64
00:03:53,872 --> 00:03:54,906
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">BASED ON THE COMIC SERIES</font>

65
00:03:54,973 --> 00:03:56,775
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>GOOD MORNING CALL
AND <i>GOOD MORNING KISS BY YUE TAKASUKA</i></i></font>

66
00:04:54,566 --> 00:04:55,967
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara didn't want to do it!</font>

67
00:04:57,535 --> 00:05:00,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I had my hopes up so high!</font>

68
00:05:01,773 --> 00:05:03,041
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

69
00:05:03,742 --> 00:05:04,943
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But look.</font>

70
00:05:05,143 --> 00:05:07,679
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao will play the princess...</font>

71
00:05:08,513 --> 00:05:09,347
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right?</font>

72
00:05:10,448 --> 00:05:11,816
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, that's right.</font>

73
00:05:11,917 --> 00:05:16,154
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it feels like a compromise,
but at least the princess is settled.</font>

74
00:05:16,254 --> 00:05:17,188
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I can get a prince...</font>

75
00:05:17,255 --> 00:05:18,290
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

76
00:05:20,392 --> 00:05:21,726
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If Uehara isn't going to do it...</font>

77
00:05:22,994 --> 00:05:24,963
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa. What are you...</font>

78
00:05:25,363 --> 00:05:26,231
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know!</font>

79
00:05:26,331 --> 00:05:29,367
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How about if you leave out
the prince and princess?</font>

80
00:05:31,369 --> 00:05:32,537
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's over.</font>

81
00:05:33,104 --> 00:05:35,240
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My once-in-a-lifetime
theatrical masterpiece...</font>

82
00:05:37,309 --> 00:05:38,343
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">is over.</font>

83
00:05:38,877 --> 00:05:40,345
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so sorry, Abe.</font>

84
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:44,516
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry, but playing a princess...</font>

85
00:05:51,823 --> 00:05:53,692
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is so lovely!</font>

86
00:05:54,559 --> 00:05:56,361
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, it totally suits you.</font>

87
00:05:57,128 --> 00:05:58,797
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You think so?</font>

88
00:05:59,264 --> 00:06:00,565
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here!</font>

89
00:06:01,333 --> 00:06:03,768
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is a tiara for a princess.</font>

90
00:06:08,073 --> 00:06:08,974
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here!</font>

91
00:06:11,910 --> 00:06:13,178
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Perfect.</font>

92
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,280
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How cute!</font>

93
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:18,483
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But why are you making costumes
for the drama department, Ota?</font>

94
00:06:19,718 --> 00:06:22,620
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe asked me. He said he needed help.</font>

95
00:06:23,088 --> 00:06:25,390
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And, since he doesn't have enough people,</font>

96
00:06:25,824 --> 00:06:27,225
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll be playing the witch.</font>

97
00:06:27,692 --> 00:06:30,028
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ota, you're going to be the witch?</font>

98
00:06:31,096 --> 00:06:32,063
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

99
00:06:33,198 --> 00:06:34,332
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

100
00:06:34,899 --> 00:06:38,303
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So Nao, why don't we do it together?</font>

101
00:06:39,504 --> 00:06:40,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think you're the only one</font>

102
00:06:40,872 --> 00:06:43,608
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that could pull off
wearing such a lovely dress, Nao.</font>

103
00:06:56,521 --> 00:06:57,889
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

104
00:06:59,391 --> 00:07:01,292
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now if I could just cast
the role of the prince...</font>

105
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,528
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who can do it?</font>

106
00:07:03,628 --> 00:07:07,032
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shall I try to persuade Uehara
one more time?</font>

107
00:07:07,132 --> 00:07:09,934
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's okay. I won't ask you
for any more help, Yoshikawa.</font>

108
00:07:12,303 --> 00:07:15,106
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since it's a prince,
he has to be handsome, right?</font>

109
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:16,708
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Someone who is refined.</font>

110
00:07:18,309 --> 00:07:22,714
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes! Someone who is thoughtful,
gentlemanly, and smells nice.</font>

111
00:07:23,948 --> 00:07:24,849
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe so.</font>

112
00:07:25,683 --> 00:07:27,085
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Someone who would make all the girls</font>

113
00:07:27,185 --> 00:07:30,288
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">scream "Prince!"
and make their eyes sparkle!</font>

114
00:07:31,623 --> 00:07:34,692
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But is there anyone other than Uehara
who could do that?</font>

115
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:37,495
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes! There is!</font>

116
00:07:38,696 --> 00:07:39,931
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just leave it to me.</font>

117
00:07:43,701 --> 00:07:44,803
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please.</font>

118
00:07:45,503 --> 00:07:46,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

119
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:51,443
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have handball practice every day.</font>

120
00:07:51,676 --> 00:07:54,012
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I'm no good at performing
in front of people like that.</font>

121
00:07:56,347 --> 00:07:57,715
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

122
00:07:58,416 --> 00:07:59,717
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about Uehara?</font>

123
00:08:01,319 --> 00:08:03,321
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess he'd never agree
to something like this.</font>

124
00:08:04,556 --> 00:08:06,024
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Exactly.</font>

125
00:08:07,358 --> 00:08:09,427
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There you are, Daichi.</font>

126
00:08:09,527 --> 00:08:10,528
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanase.</font>

127
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:16,134
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, if I find someone interested,</font>

128
00:08:16,234 --> 00:08:18,403
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll ask them for you, so hang in there.</font>

129
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:20,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay. Thank you, Daichi.</font>

130
00:08:21,339 --> 00:08:23,007
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-See you.
-Sure.</font>

131
00:08:31,483 --> 00:08:35,386
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It really is one thing after another
when it comes to Nao.</font>

132
00:08:37,755 --> 00:08:38,756
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

133
00:08:44,929 --> 00:08:45,897
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey.</font>

134
00:08:46,731 --> 00:08:47,732
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

135
00:08:49,701 --> 00:08:50,602
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here.</font>

136
00:08:51,836 --> 00:08:53,071
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's this?</font>

137
00:08:53,638 --> 00:08:56,407
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a present to congratulate you
for winning the tournament.</font>

138
00:08:56,708 --> 00:08:59,410
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you serious?
What's this about all of a sudden?</font>

139
00:08:59,511 --> 00:09:02,714
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a manager's duty to encourage
the ace of the team.</font>

140
00:09:02,814 --> 00:09:04,682
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's what makes you
such a great manager.</font>

141
00:09:04,782 --> 00:09:05,917
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What could it be?</font>

142
00:09:08,753 --> 00:09:11,022
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow. How nice!</font>

143
00:09:11,723 --> 00:09:13,725
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you. I really appreciate this.</font>

144
00:09:23,635 --> 00:09:25,703
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So Daichi is a bust too.</font>

145
00:09:28,806 --> 00:09:32,610
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Handicrafts again, Natsume? It's boring!</font>

146
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:34,812
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Let's go for some tea.
-That's a good idea, right?</font>

147
00:09:34,913 --> 00:09:35,780
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please!</font>

148
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:37,015
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go next time.</font>

149
00:09:37,081 --> 00:09:38,783
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's great!</font>

150
00:09:41,119 --> 00:09:42,453
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Another option.</font>

151
00:09:43,855 --> 00:09:46,090
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry. I could never do it.</font>

152
00:09:47,959 --> 00:09:51,529
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-He shot it down with a smile on his face.
-Working in a group doesn't suit me.</font>

153
00:09:51,596 --> 00:09:54,632
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really should try
to persuade Uehara again.</font>

154
00:09:55,567 --> 00:09:56,935
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you think you can do it somehow?</font>

155
00:09:58,336 --> 00:10:00,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll try until I succeed.</font>

156
00:10:00,838 --> 00:10:05,877
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi and Natsume are cool guys too,
but Uehara would be the perfect prince.</font>

157
00:10:05,977 --> 00:10:07,045
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can play the prince.</font>

158
00:10:10,381 --> 00:10:12,317
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That is, if the girl playing
the princess is cute.</font>

159
00:10:20,959 --> 00:10:22,594
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's you, Nao?
-Yes.</font>

160
00:10:25,096 --> 00:10:26,698
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This keeps happening.</font>

161
00:10:29,167 --> 00:10:32,737
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess I'm not good enough, huh?</font>

162
00:10:33,671 --> 00:10:34,739
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't say that...</font>

163
00:10:34,806 --> 00:10:37,342
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes! We have our prince!</font>

164
00:10:37,408 --> 00:10:39,110
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Natsume!</font>

165
00:10:39,377 --> 00:10:42,847
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now these costumes will finally
see the light of day.</font>

166
00:10:45,350 --> 00:10:48,286
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The prince and princess meet,
their identities hidden from each other.</font>

167
00:10:48,386 --> 00:10:50,655
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They fall deeply in love at first sight!</font>

168
00:10:50,955 --> 00:10:54,359
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But their two nations are hostile enemies.</font>

169
00:10:54,492 --> 00:10:55,426
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's Romeo and Juliet.</font>

170
00:10:55,493 --> 00:10:56,995
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The pair are forced to separate!</font>

171
00:10:57,095 --> 00:10:58,396
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How awful!</font>

172
00:10:58,796 --> 00:11:01,633
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And then they face a new hardship!</font>

173
00:11:02,467 --> 00:11:07,038
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A witch who is jealous of the princess
curses her into an eternal sleep!</font>

174
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:16,748
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Only a man who loves you
with all his heart can lift the curse.</font>

175
00:11:17,615 --> 00:11:20,718
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Will such a man ever appear?</font>

176
00:11:24,355 --> 00:11:25,657
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ota, why are you so good at this?</font>

177
00:11:25,723 --> 00:11:28,793
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Time passes!
The prince learns of the curse</font>

178
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,595
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and runs to her.</font>

179
00:11:31,195 --> 00:11:34,365
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He abandons his country and his identity,</font>

180
00:11:34,932 --> 00:11:39,203
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">all for the one princess he loves.</font>

181
00:11:40,772 --> 00:11:41,973
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How lovely!</font>

182
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:45,176
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is a story woven
by a man and a woman,</font>

183
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:50,181
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">the story of a love so terribly pure.</font>

184
00:11:57,989 --> 00:12:00,391
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe, I'll do my best to play the princess!</font>

185
00:12:00,491 --> 00:12:01,826
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's the spirit, Yoshikawa!</font>

186
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:05,530
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We better get ready to practice, Natsume.</font>

187
00:12:08,399 --> 00:12:09,367
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

188
00:12:12,570 --> 00:12:13,871
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

189
00:12:19,577 --> 00:12:21,279
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

190
00:12:21,446 --> 00:12:26,451
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why must you be a prince of Tontague?</font>

191
00:12:27,352 --> 00:12:29,253
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The same goes for you, princess.</font>

192
00:12:30,154 --> 00:12:31,923
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you from the nation of Caplet?</font>

193
00:12:33,925 --> 00:12:35,593
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, Uehara. Are we too loud?</font>

194
00:12:35,893 --> 00:12:37,128
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're asking now?</font>

195
00:12:37,795 --> 00:12:39,230
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you in my place anyway?</font>

196
00:12:39,297 --> 00:12:40,698
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You could do this at Yoshikawa's.</font>

197
00:12:40,765 --> 00:12:42,900
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No men other than you are allowed
at her place, right?</font>

198
00:12:51,909 --> 00:12:53,678
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Prince!</font>

199
00:12:53,778 --> 00:12:55,246
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My sun!</font>

200
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:59,484
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Days without you are like being cast
into total darkness.</font>

201
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:00,685
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You call that acting?</font>

202
00:13:00,752 --> 00:13:03,254
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It is the same for me, beautiful princess.</font>

203
00:13:03,955 --> 00:13:06,190
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It is your destiny to live by my side.</font>

204
00:13:06,257 --> 00:13:07,725
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And he's a gigolo.</font>

205
00:13:07,792 --> 00:13:09,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't make that sad face,</font>

206
00:13:09,927 --> 00:13:11,062
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and please smile for me.</font>

207
00:13:12,864 --> 00:13:13,998
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Prince!</font>

208
00:13:14,665 --> 00:13:16,467
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">To that smile of yours...</font>

209
00:13:16,567 --> 00:13:17,702
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I need something to drink.</font>

210
00:13:17,802 --> 00:13:18,870
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I swear eternal love.</font>

211
00:13:18,970 --> 00:13:20,071
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Out of the way.</font>

212
00:13:23,074 --> 00:13:25,943
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Why did you deliberately come
between us like that?</font>

213
00:13:26,043 --> 00:13:27,879
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can go wherever I want, can't I?</font>

214
00:13:27,979 --> 00:13:29,347
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so obvious!</font>

215
00:13:30,982 --> 00:13:32,483
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's do it again, Natsume.</font>

216
00:13:32,683 --> 00:13:33,751
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, then...</font>

217
00:13:34,185 --> 00:13:35,987
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't make a sad face,</font>

218
00:13:36,587 --> 00:13:37,789
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and please smile for me.</font>

219
00:13:40,958 --> 00:13:42,193
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He did it again.</font>

220
00:13:43,461 --> 00:13:45,396
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go around this way!</font>

221
00:13:45,496 --> 00:13:47,198
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. That's the shortest way through.</font>

222
00:13:48,166 --> 00:13:51,169
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The shortest way is here like this!</font>

223
00:13:51,903 --> 00:13:52,904
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Get it?</font>

224
00:13:53,004 --> 00:13:55,406
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is why you're bad at math.</font>

225
00:13:56,774 --> 00:13:58,976
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But the fridge is there,
so if you go around like...</font>

226
00:13:59,076 --> 00:14:00,611
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. I get up this way.</font>

227
00:14:00,678 --> 00:14:02,346
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-So just move your chair!
-Then I have to...</font>

228
00:14:02,447 --> 00:14:03,781
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Move!
-Okay.</font>

229
00:14:03,981 --> 00:14:06,017
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll never finish
if you keep going on like this.</font>

230
00:14:06,117 --> 00:14:08,486
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's still a lot left
before the final kissing scene.</font>

231
00:14:11,389 --> 00:14:12,256
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Kissing scene?</font>

232
00:14:19,163 --> 00:14:20,798
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THE PAIR GENTLY TOUCH LIPS AND KISS.</font>

233
00:14:23,201 --> 00:14:25,069
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You didn't read it through the end?</font>

234
00:14:27,572 --> 00:14:28,439
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

235
00:14:29,273 --> 00:14:31,442
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it's written in the script,</font>

236
00:14:31,909 --> 00:14:33,077
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so we'll have to kiss.</font>

237
00:14:38,049 --> 00:14:39,717
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm kidding.</font>

238
00:14:39,817 --> 00:14:42,119
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They mostly fake the kisses
for stuff like this.</font>

239
00:14:47,792 --> 00:14:48,793
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

240
00:14:48,893 --> 00:14:50,127
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course.</font>

241
00:14:51,429 --> 00:14:53,798
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Three days before opening</font>

242
00:14:58,536 --> 00:15:00,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're in trouble. We're in big trouble.</font>

243
00:15:02,006 --> 00:15:04,308
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">One of them is clearly terrible.</font>

244
00:15:04,475 --> 00:15:07,078
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-The other one is too much of a flirt.
-That was so good, wasn't it?</font>

245
00:15:07,879 --> 00:15:10,681
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Could you at least
learn your lines, Yoshikawa?</font>

246
00:15:10,781 --> 00:15:13,184
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was my best performance yet!</font>

247
00:15:13,251 --> 00:15:14,519
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

248
00:15:15,419 --> 00:15:16,621
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe?</font>

249
00:15:17,355 --> 00:15:19,190
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Right, Natsume?
-Yes.</font>

250
00:15:23,828 --> 00:15:24,662
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina?</font>

251
00:15:35,006 --> 00:15:37,141
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You might break up with Mitsuishi?</font>

252
00:15:42,547 --> 00:15:45,283
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why? How come?</font>

253
00:15:46,450 --> 00:15:49,620
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Things haven't been going well
for a while lately.</font>

254
00:15:50,555 --> 00:15:52,924
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even on the phone,
he always seems so busy.</font>

255
00:15:53,024 --> 00:15:54,759
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We end up sort of arguing every time.</font>

256
00:15:56,661 --> 00:16:00,097
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he's studying to be a vet.
That would make him busy, right?</font>

257
00:16:00,998 --> 00:16:02,466
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That is true.</font>

258
00:16:03,701 --> 00:16:06,938
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I feel like I'm the only one waiting.
It makes me feel uncertain.</font>

259
00:16:08,306 --> 00:16:11,642
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And when I called a week ago,
a girl picked up.</font>

260
00:16:14,812 --> 00:16:18,082
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was just someone
he works with in the lab, though.</font>

261
00:16:21,652 --> 00:16:27,425
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I was so frustrated, and I said
a lot of terrible things to him.</font>

262
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:30,795
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then...</font>

263
00:16:31,262 --> 00:16:34,398
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">he said, "You don't trust me, Marina."</font>

264
00:16:37,134 --> 00:16:39,704
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And I said, "You're right,"
and that was the end of it.</font>

265
00:16:48,913 --> 00:16:53,017
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>SLEEPING BEAUTY
WRITER-DIRECTOR JUN ABE</i></font>

266
00:17:01,692 --> 00:17:05,796
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your girlfriend and your friend
are playing lovers.</font>

267
00:17:08,632 --> 00:17:10,534
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It could plant the seeds of love.</font>

268
00:17:11,636 --> 00:17:12,570
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

269
00:17:13,137 --> 00:17:14,739
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a total comedy.</font>

270
00:17:15,239 --> 00:17:20,378
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It says, "The ultimate romantic tragedy
woven by lovers with entwined destinies."</font>

271
00:17:20,478 --> 00:17:22,013
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. It's a comedy.</font>

272
00:17:23,881 --> 00:17:25,182
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

273
00:17:27,084 --> 00:17:31,789
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"The ultimate romance"
sure sounds good though.</font>

274
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:37,128
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

275
00:17:37,728 --> 00:17:40,498
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't expect you'd say such a thing.</font>

276
00:17:40,564 --> 00:17:46,370
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How rude. Even I dream
of living my life with someone someday.</font>

277
00:17:48,305 --> 00:17:50,441
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Someone that could live with you, Saeko?</font>

278
00:17:50,908 --> 00:17:52,576
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you trying to say no one would?</font>

279
00:17:52,643 --> 00:17:55,613
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think it's a pretty narrow list.</font>

280
00:18:00,184 --> 00:18:03,254
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come to think of it, someone like you
might be good for me, Uehara.</font>

281
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:05,923
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You accept my work, and you don't seem
like you would be too clingy.</font>

282
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:07,391
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What am I saying?</font>

283
00:18:09,260 --> 00:18:10,761
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I suppose so.</font>

284
00:18:18,269 --> 00:18:23,340
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">YOU HAVE A NEW MESSAGE FROM
"ACQUAINTANCE?"</font>

285
00:18:28,579 --> 00:18:32,049
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry. I'll get going first.</font>

286
00:18:44,462 --> 00:18:45,896
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So this is the place?</font>

287
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:51,869
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You and Nao are doing well, Uehara.</font>

288
00:18:53,137 --> 00:18:55,139
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's so nostalgic,
I feel like I'm going to cry.</font>

289
00:18:55,206 --> 00:18:57,742
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">UEHARA</font>

290
00:18:59,877 --> 00:19:04,348
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa joined a handicrafts club.</font>

291
00:19:06,617 --> 00:19:08,285
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She hasn't changed a bit.</font>

292
00:19:09,286 --> 00:19:10,321
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

293
00:19:11,522 --> 00:19:13,557
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We were always laughing together</font>

294
00:19:15,259 --> 00:19:17,094
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">back in the day.</font>

295
00:19:20,131 --> 00:19:23,000
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, you need to have
a real talk with her.</font>

296
00:19:23,534 --> 00:19:27,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Seriously. What do you think I should do?</font>

297
00:19:29,206 --> 00:19:31,542
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do I do if she says
she wants to break up?</font>

298
00:19:32,143 --> 00:19:34,078
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The first thing to do is to just
sit down and talk.</font>

299
00:19:34,345 --> 00:19:36,447
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa? She's back early.</font>

300
00:19:37,314 --> 00:19:38,682
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait a second!</font>

301
00:19:38,949 --> 00:19:39,784
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What will you say?</font>

302
00:19:39,850 --> 00:19:40,918
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll tell Yoshikawa that...</font>

303
00:19:41,018 --> 00:19:44,155
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Marina. I have some tasty cakes.</font>

304
00:19:46,190 --> 00:19:47,758
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really should head home.</font>

305
00:19:50,461 --> 00:19:52,363
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for listening to me
about everything.</font>

306
00:19:57,802 --> 00:19:59,170
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Listen, Marina.</font>

307
00:19:59,870 --> 00:20:01,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Should I try talking to Mitsuishi?</font>

308
00:20:04,341 --> 00:20:06,677
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I feel like it's better
to break it off clean</font>

309
00:20:07,077 --> 00:20:09,046
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">rather than both of us
just feeling worse and worse.</font>

310
00:20:12,416 --> 00:20:15,653
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But Marina, Mitsuishi really...</font>

311
00:20:15,719 --> 00:20:17,021
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe I should find someone else.</font>

312
00:20:18,956 --> 00:20:20,991
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi is not the only man out there.</font>

313
00:20:21,292 --> 00:20:22,359
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you.</font>

314
00:20:24,695 --> 00:20:25,763
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina.</font>

315
00:20:42,813 --> 00:20:43,814
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

316
00:20:45,015 --> 00:20:46,116
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was the finishing blow.</font>

317
00:20:46,817 --> 00:20:47,885
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You heard that?</font>

318
00:20:47,985 --> 00:20:50,421
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it wasn't just me that overheard.</font>

319
00:20:57,294 --> 00:20:58,829
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi?</font>

320
00:21:03,267 --> 00:21:04,969
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do we do?</font>

321
00:21:11,075 --> 00:21:12,076
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Marina.</i></font>

322
00:21:17,815 --> 00:21:19,817
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We can't just leave things like this.</font>

323
00:21:30,728 --> 00:21:32,196
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>SLEEPING BEAUTY
WRITER-DIRECTOR JUN ABE</i></font>

324
00:21:32,796 --> 00:21:33,864
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

325
00:21:36,333 --> 00:21:37,534
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is it.</font>

326
00:21:38,636 --> 00:21:39,904
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This has to be it.</font>

327
00:21:40,437 --> 00:21:41,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Hey!</i></font>

328
00:21:41,538 --> 00:21:42,973
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What if we swapped in</font>

329
00:21:43,073 --> 00:21:45,409
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina and Mitsuishi
for the prince and princess?</font>

330
00:21:46,443 --> 00:21:48,812
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

331
00:21:49,647 --> 00:21:51,649
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If they really look each other
in the eyes and talk,</font>

332
00:21:51,749 --> 00:21:53,817
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it could resolve
bad feelings between them.</font>

333
00:21:56,620 --> 00:21:59,189
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sure it'll work. What do you think?</font>

334
00:22:00,991 --> 00:22:03,427
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think it's best if we don't interfere.</font>

335
00:22:05,796 --> 00:22:06,630
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

336
00:22:07,097 --> 00:22:10,601
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it's better for them
to resolve things by themselves.</font>

337
00:22:12,069 --> 00:22:12,937
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But...</font>

338
00:22:17,841 --> 00:22:21,578
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't think Marina really wants
to break up with Mitsuishi.</font>

339
00:22:24,148 --> 00:22:25,716
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You would know it if you saw her face.</font>

340
00:22:32,756 --> 00:22:34,725
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's best for them</font>

341
00:22:35,726 --> 00:22:37,594
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">is for them to decide, isn't it?</font>

342
00:22:41,265 --> 00:22:43,400
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If everything could be decided
by one person,</font>

343
00:22:43,467 --> 00:22:45,336
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">no one would ever ask for advice.</font>

344
00:22:46,036 --> 00:22:48,372
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina and Mitsuishi came to talk to us</font>

345
00:22:48,472 --> 00:22:50,641
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">because they couldn't decide things
for themselves.</font>

346
00:23:13,163 --> 00:23:14,631
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget it.</font>

347
00:23:21,772 --> 00:23:22,773
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey.</font>

348
00:23:33,317 --> 00:23:34,551
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao?</font>

349
00:23:39,356 --> 00:23:41,792
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong? Aren't we rehearsing?</font>

350
00:23:47,631 --> 00:23:48,932
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

351
00:23:53,070 --> 00:23:57,574
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, to be honest, I agree with Uehara.</font>

352
00:24:00,044 --> 00:24:01,612
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe because I'm a man.</font>

353
00:24:03,013 --> 00:24:05,682
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sometimes I want something
to help make things right again,</font>

354
00:24:05,749 --> 00:24:07,918
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but in the end, I would want
to decide things on our own.</font>

355
00:24:08,852 --> 00:24:11,155
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess I don't want others
to tell us what to do.</font>

356
00:24:11,522 --> 00:24:13,123
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wouldn't want them to interfere.</font>

357
00:24:18,796 --> 00:24:19,963
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

358
00:24:21,732 --> 00:24:24,101
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess that's one way of looking at it.</font>

359
00:24:27,738 --> 00:24:31,442
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That seems like a grown-up way
of being in a relationship.</font>

360
00:24:34,912 --> 00:24:35,846
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

361
00:24:37,915 --> 00:24:40,617
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't need to force yourself
to become an adult.</font>

362
00:24:43,320 --> 00:24:44,354
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

363
00:24:45,589 --> 00:24:47,958
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're still a little kid.</font>

364
00:24:51,528 --> 00:24:53,497
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want to hear that
from you, Uehara!</font>

365
00:24:55,899 --> 00:24:58,502
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, what do you want to do?</font>

366
00:25:02,639 --> 00:25:03,740
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

367
00:25:06,877 --> 00:25:10,280
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want
Marina and Mitsuishi to break up.</font>

368
00:25:10,747 --> 00:25:13,117
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to do whatever I can to help.</font>

369
00:25:15,152 --> 00:25:17,421
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Neither of them are really smiling.</font>

370
00:25:18,589 --> 00:25:21,191
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The only one that can make
Marina smile is Mitsuishi,</font>

371
00:25:21,291 --> 00:25:24,094
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and the only one that
can make Mitsuishi smile is Marina.</font>

372
00:25:39,543 --> 00:25:40,410
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So shall we do it?</font>

373
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:47,551
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really, Uehara?</font>

374
00:25:48,252 --> 00:25:49,086
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure.</font>

375
00:25:51,955 --> 00:25:52,956
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Alright!</font>

376
00:25:59,363 --> 00:26:00,464
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

377
00:26:11,175 --> 00:26:13,177
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shall I help too, princess?</font>

378
00:26:16,146 --> 00:26:17,114
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You too, Natsume?</font>

379
00:26:17,447 --> 00:26:18,715
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yes.
-Really?</font>

380
00:26:20,684 --> 00:26:23,520
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I feel like this is going to go great.</font>

381
00:26:24,188 --> 00:26:27,491
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, we need to tell Mitsuishi right away.</font>

382
00:26:30,928 --> 00:26:31,995
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi!</font>

383
00:26:32,863 --> 00:26:33,730
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi!</font>

384
00:26:35,499 --> 00:26:37,267
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi!</font>

385
00:26:37,601 --> 00:26:38,869
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Special training starts today.</font>

386
00:26:38,969 --> 00:26:40,037
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For what?</font>

387
00:26:40,103 --> 00:26:42,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi, you're going to play a prince.</font>

388
00:26:43,073 --> 00:26:44,308
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A prince.</font>

389
00:26:44,708 --> 00:26:46,243
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Back to her usual self?</font>

390
00:26:47,177 --> 00:26:48,078
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

391
00:26:48,345 --> 00:26:51,248
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In any case, I hope it goes well.</font>

392
00:26:51,915 --> 00:26:52,749
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right.</font>

393
00:26:52,816 --> 00:26:54,451
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just remembered.</font>

394
00:26:54,551 --> 00:26:57,454
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao and I have to prepare,
so you look after him, Uehara.</font>

395
00:27:00,324 --> 00:27:04,027
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OPENING DAY</font>

396
00:27:05,729 --> 00:27:07,931
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>SLEEPING BEAUTY</i></font>

397
00:27:07,998 --> 00:27:09,233
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They've got so many posters up.</font>

398
00:27:09,333 --> 00:27:10,267
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right, wow.</font>

399
00:27:10,367 --> 00:27:12,102
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait. Written and directed by Abe?</font>

400
00:27:12,202 --> 00:27:13,470
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe? Seriously?</font>

401
00:27:27,551 --> 00:27:29,553
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry for suddenly asking you
for this favor, Marina.</font>

402
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:32,522
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't be. I'll be cheering you on,
so go break a leg.</font>

403
00:27:32,589 --> 00:27:33,857
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

404
00:27:42,299 --> 00:27:43,800
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi, are you ready?</font>

405
00:27:45,235 --> 00:27:47,437
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes. Leave it to me.</font>

406
00:27:48,071 --> 00:27:49,373
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll be fine.</font>

407
00:27:50,807 --> 00:27:52,509
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You'll be great. I'm sure of it.</font>

408
00:27:53,710 --> 00:27:54,945
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can do this, Mitsuishi.</font>

409
00:28:04,721 --> 00:28:10,060
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>We now present the Tokyo Meiken University
drama workshop's Sleeping Beauty.</i></font>

410
00:28:10,627 --> 00:28:12,562
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Written and directed by Jun Abe.</i></font>

411
00:28:13,397 --> 00:28:15,866
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>We will now start the play
produced by Jun Abe.</i></font>

412
00:28:16,667 --> 00:28:19,870
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>We hope you enjoy the show until the end.</i></font>

413
00:28:55,839 --> 00:28:57,274
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Prince!</font>

414
00:29:02,412 --> 00:29:03,380
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

415
00:29:04,881 --> 00:29:10,387
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">On that day, enveloped by warm sunlight
filtering through the trees...</font>

416
00:29:14,491 --> 00:29:15,926
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Through the trees...</font>

417
00:29:20,430 --> 00:29:22,232
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What was it?
-Her very first line!</font>

418
00:29:22,299 --> 00:29:24,735
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How many times did I tell her
to memorize them!</font>

419
00:29:27,504 --> 00:29:28,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's it!</font>

420
00:29:28,739 --> 00:29:31,308
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why is she speaking every thought?
-In this place</font>

421
00:29:31,375 --> 00:29:33,610
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">where the violets are in full bloom...</font>

422
00:29:34,444 --> 00:29:35,278
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Princess!</font>

423
00:29:35,879 --> 00:29:38,615
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have never seen true beauty
until this moment.</font>

424
00:29:39,082 --> 00:29:40,851
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abracadabra!</font>

425
00:29:40,917 --> 00:29:43,453
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abracadabra!</font>

426
00:29:43,887 --> 00:29:45,455
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Alakazam!</font>

427
00:29:46,723 --> 00:29:51,828
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And only a man who loves you
with all his heart can lift the curse.</font>

428
00:29:52,396 --> 00:29:55,232
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Will such a man ever appear?</font>

429
00:30:01,505 --> 00:30:06,443
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm feeling so faint!</font>

430
00:30:20,457 --> 00:30:23,093
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There will now be
a 15-minute intermission.</font>

431
00:30:31,268 --> 00:30:32,969
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Nao?</font>

432
00:30:33,637 --> 00:30:36,640
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you okay? Is it your stomach?
Does your stomach hurt?</font>

433
00:30:36,740 --> 00:30:37,874
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't take it!</font>

434
00:30:40,277 --> 00:30:41,645
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina, please.</font>

435
00:30:45,282 --> 00:30:49,419
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please play the princess in my place.</font>

436
00:30:49,886 --> 00:30:52,422
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hang on. You can't just ask me to...</font>

437
00:30:52,489 --> 00:30:56,193
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You'll be okay. You just need
to sleep in the coffin. Okay?</font>

438
00:30:56,259 --> 00:30:57,727
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Okay"? It's not that easy.</font>

439
00:30:57,794 --> 00:30:59,930
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina.</font>

440
00:31:09,139 --> 00:31:11,208
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">HANDICRAFTS CLUB</font>

441
00:31:28,058 --> 00:31:29,326
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi.</font>

442
00:31:36,333 --> 00:31:37,200
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi?</font>

443
00:31:37,267 --> 00:31:38,902
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao. It's almost time.</font>

444
00:31:43,874 --> 00:31:44,975
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did he run away?</font>

445
00:31:54,818 --> 00:31:56,186
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi!</font>

446
00:31:57,554 --> 00:31:58,421
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi!</font>

447
00:31:58,522 --> 00:31:59,589
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa.</font>

448
00:32:04,895 --> 00:32:07,063
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe he got nervous.</font>

449
00:32:09,065 --> 00:32:11,501
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, that's that then.</font>

450
00:32:11,601 --> 00:32:12,869
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Idiot.</font>

451
00:32:15,872 --> 00:32:17,207
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry so much.</font>

452
00:32:19,075 --> 00:32:21,177
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I promise I'll find him
and bring him back.</font>

453
00:32:22,679 --> 00:32:25,916
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">After all that practice, you think
I'll put up with him running away?</font>

454
00:32:27,851 --> 00:32:28,685
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

455
00:32:28,752 --> 00:32:29,920
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So,</font>

456
00:32:32,856 --> 00:32:36,493
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you just have faith in me and wait.</font>

457
00:32:39,062 --> 00:32:40,196
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That is all.</font>

458
00:32:41,765 --> 00:32:43,266
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

459
00:32:49,072 --> 00:32:50,173
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Please wait for me.</i></font>

460
00:32:50,707 --> 00:32:53,209
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even if you are across the ocean,</font>

461
00:32:53,777 --> 00:32:55,445
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will reach you, I swear.</font>

462
00:33:05,989 --> 00:33:07,123
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll be okay.</font>

463
00:33:08,325 --> 00:33:10,126
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara is a man who does
what needs to be done.</font>

464
00:33:12,562 --> 00:33:13,563
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay.</font>

465
00:33:17,067 --> 00:33:18,602
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sure it will go well.</font>

466
00:33:19,836 --> 00:33:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will have faith in Uehara, and wait.</font>

467
00:33:24,608 --> 00:33:31,615
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">HANDICRAFTS CLUB
THIS WAY</font>

468
00:33:48,098 --> 00:33:52,802
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And 65 sheep, and 66 sheep,</font>

469
00:33:52,869 --> 00:33:56,139
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and 67 sheep, and 68 sheep,</font>

470
00:33:56,239 --> 00:34:00,210
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and 69 sheep, and 70 sheep,</font>

471
00:34:00,377 --> 00:34:02,045
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and 71 sheep...</font>

472
00:34:04,981 --> 00:34:06,516
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm done with.</font>

473
00:34:07,817 --> 00:34:09,319
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's all over.</font>

474
00:34:12,689 --> 00:34:15,592
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There you are.
What the hell are you doing?</font>

475
00:34:16,326 --> 00:34:17,394
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No!</font>

476
00:34:18,294 --> 00:34:19,129
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

477
00:34:20,864 --> 00:34:21,898
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

478
00:34:23,033 --> 00:34:24,934
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Mitsuishi!</font>

479
00:34:25,435 --> 00:34:27,037
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Pull yourself together, and get out here.</font>

480
00:34:27,137 --> 00:34:29,706
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, what are you doing here?</font>

481
00:34:30,140 --> 00:34:31,374
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no time.</font>

482
00:34:31,441 --> 00:34:32,475
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go.</font>

483
00:34:33,076 --> 00:34:34,544
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Go"? But...</font>

484
00:34:34,644 --> 00:34:38,314
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are the two of you so pushy?</font>

485
00:34:39,883 --> 00:34:41,718
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop moaning.</font>

486
00:34:42,152 --> 00:34:44,387
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Locking yourself in there
isn't going to change anything.</font>

487
00:34:44,454 --> 00:34:45,555
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just leave me alone!</font>

488
00:34:45,689 --> 00:34:46,790
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">As if I could!</font>

489
00:34:51,795 --> 00:34:53,463
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you two don't patch things up,</font>

490
00:34:54,698 --> 00:34:58,268
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yoshikawa will go crazy trying to fix it,
and that'll be a headache for me.</font>

491
00:35:01,538 --> 00:35:03,807
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi!</font>

492
00:35:04,340 --> 00:35:05,742
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you listening to me?</font>

493
00:35:07,577 --> 00:35:08,845
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Gosh.</font>

494
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:13,883
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I knew it.
Nao is the most important, right?</font>

495
00:35:30,834 --> 00:35:32,736
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really haven't changed a bit.</font>

496
00:35:34,637 --> 00:35:36,139
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's kind of amazing.</font>

497
00:35:39,776 --> 00:35:41,611
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you two any different?</font>

498
00:35:45,348 --> 00:35:47,050
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did anything change about you?</font>

499
00:35:51,121 --> 00:35:53,056
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Princess!</font>

500
00:35:57,093 --> 00:35:59,395
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do I really only have to just lie here?</font>

501
00:36:02,832 --> 00:36:04,100
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who are you?</font>

502
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:07,237
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the prince of Tontague.
What are you doing here?</font>

503
00:36:08,438 --> 00:36:11,908
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't worry.
I'll wake you with a perfect kiss.</font>

504
00:36:12,575 --> 00:36:17,413
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Will Natsume really kiss me?</font>

505
00:36:39,035 --> 00:36:40,003
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No!</font>

506
00:36:45,642 --> 00:36:46,543
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi?</font>

507
00:36:51,047 --> 00:36:52,582
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So we were just in time.</font>

508
00:36:53,049 --> 00:36:54,684
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina and Mitsuishi?</font>

509
00:36:56,119 --> 00:36:56,953
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's happening?</font>

510
00:37:04,994 --> 00:37:08,131
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you've finally awoken, my beloved.</font>

511
00:37:16,206 --> 00:37:17,240
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Prince.</font>

512
00:37:18,007 --> 00:37:20,176
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing here?</font>

513
00:37:21,511 --> 00:37:24,681
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I learned of the curse
the witch put on you,</font>

514
00:37:25,148 --> 00:37:27,884
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and came at once by horse,
for three days and three nights.</font>

515
00:37:31,054 --> 00:37:32,288
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please forgive me</font>

516
00:37:33,356 --> 00:37:35,391
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">for making you wait</font>

517
00:37:37,527 --> 00:37:38,928
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">for so long.</font>

518
00:37:43,333 --> 00:37:44,968
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No matter how far apart we were,</font>

519
00:37:45,635 --> 00:37:47,937
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">my love for you never changed.</font>

520
00:37:50,607 --> 00:37:51,808
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Morning,</font>

521
00:37:52,575 --> 00:37:53,509
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">noon,</font>

522
00:37:54,477 --> 00:37:55,545
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">night,</font>

523
00:37:56,613 --> 00:37:57,480
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you are the only...</font>

524
00:37:57,580 --> 00:37:58,615
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's enough.</font>

525
00:38:00,750 --> 00:38:01,584
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

526
00:38:04,187 --> 00:38:05,321
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You see,</font>

527
00:38:06,689 --> 00:38:07,690
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just exhausted.</font>

528
00:38:12,829 --> 00:38:14,130
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was all just me.</font>

529
00:38:15,098 --> 00:38:17,300
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I got happy, I got lonely, I got worried.</font>

530
00:38:18,234 --> 00:38:20,303
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It might be nothing to you, Mitsuishi,</font>

531
00:38:20,670 --> 00:38:23,473
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but it makes me a mess inside
in an instant.</font>

532
00:38:27,577 --> 00:38:29,545
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And to keep waiting for you
while I feel this way...</font>

533
00:38:31,848 --> 00:38:33,483
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, it's pretty hard.</font>

534
00:38:35,518 --> 00:38:36,586
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So...</font>

535
00:38:45,962 --> 00:38:47,430
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

536
00:38:49,966 --> 00:38:50,800
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

537
00:38:52,769 --> 00:38:54,337
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

538
00:38:55,338 --> 00:38:57,674
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you acting like
you're the only one who's lonely?</font>

539
00:38:57,774 --> 00:39:00,643
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like you're the only one who is suffering!</font>

540
00:39:03,179 --> 00:39:04,380
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

541
00:39:05,949 --> 00:39:08,751
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wanted to see you too, Marina.</font>

542
00:39:09,485 --> 00:39:12,889
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to hold you and always be together.</font>

543
00:39:14,290 --> 00:39:16,559
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm a man.</font>

544
00:39:18,127 --> 00:39:20,797
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's incredibly hard for me
to say those things.</font>

545
00:39:27,537 --> 00:39:30,173
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

546
00:39:32,809 --> 00:39:34,010
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So...</font>

547
00:39:36,546 --> 00:39:42,952
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no need for you
to feel uneasy or anything.</font>

548
00:39:48,124 --> 00:39:49,258
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

549
00:39:53,663 --> 00:39:55,064
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did it...</font>

550
00:39:58,634 --> 00:39:59,936
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did it go well?</font>

551
00:40:03,806 --> 00:40:04,674
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

552
00:40:07,076 --> 00:40:09,178
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara! We did it!</font>

553
00:40:10,980 --> 00:40:12,548
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Be quiet!</font>

554
00:40:12,982 --> 00:40:14,017
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Quiet! Look!</font>

555
00:40:14,117 --> 00:40:16,285
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have no idea what's going on!</font>

556
00:40:16,886 --> 00:40:20,356
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But we can't just let things
end like this, right?</font>

557
00:40:21,891 --> 00:40:22,725
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Okay!</font>

558
00:40:23,326 --> 00:40:25,328
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Prince and princess hug,
then curtain closes.</font>

559
00:40:43,679 --> 00:40:44,947
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

560
00:41:00,997 --> 00:41:03,299
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thank you very much.
-Thank you very much.</font>

561
00:41:05,968 --> 00:41:07,170
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina!</font>

562
00:41:07,270 --> 00:41:11,107
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How could you do that!
That was so embarrassing!</font>

563
00:41:11,574 --> 00:41:13,709
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry, but...</font>

564
00:41:13,810 --> 00:41:14,977
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Nao.</font>

565
00:41:21,150 --> 00:41:22,552
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina!</font>

566
00:41:22,652 --> 00:41:23,719
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

567
00:41:29,525 --> 00:41:30,893
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi, you were so cool.</font>

568
00:41:31,794 --> 00:41:32,829
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really?
-Yes.</font>

569
00:41:32,929 --> 00:41:34,630
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How embarrassing.</font>

570
00:41:34,697 --> 00:41:36,399
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you truly, Nao.</font>

571
00:41:40,970 --> 00:41:42,071
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so glad.</font>

572
00:41:42,839 --> 00:41:45,074
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's the first real smile
I've seen from you in a while.</font>

573
00:41:47,443 --> 00:41:48,978
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

574
00:41:50,413 --> 00:41:53,082
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Friends really are
the thing you need most.</font>

575
00:41:55,451 --> 00:41:56,986
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I owe you one.</font>

576
00:41:58,321 --> 00:41:59,455
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course.</font>

577
00:42:00,156 --> 00:42:03,626
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When I saw you come looking for me,
I was so moved.</font>

578
00:42:04,327 --> 00:42:06,496
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao really is your...</font>

579
00:42:07,396 --> 00:42:09,298
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This place is so dusty, isn't it?</font>

580
00:42:09,632 --> 00:42:10,600
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Indeed.</font>

581
00:42:11,767 --> 00:42:16,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, anyway, Uehara and Nao
are now our models.</font>

582
00:42:16,472 --> 00:42:19,509
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We need you two to stay as you are always.</font>

583
00:42:20,076 --> 00:42:20,910
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right!</font>

584
00:42:20,977 --> 00:42:23,479
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, that's...</font>

585
00:42:24,413 --> 00:42:25,515
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">probably...</font>

586
00:42:26,349 --> 00:42:27,483
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't that okay?</font>

587
00:42:29,385 --> 00:42:30,620
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right!</font>

588
00:42:34,257 --> 00:42:35,725
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well done!</font>

589
00:42:35,791 --> 00:42:38,528
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well done!</font>

590
00:42:38,628 --> 00:42:40,196
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is everyone coming to the after party?</font>

591
00:42:40,263 --> 00:42:42,431
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's the director's treat to celebrate
our great success!</font>

592
00:42:42,498 --> 00:42:44,467
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hooray for the director!
-How generous!</font>

593
00:42:44,567 --> 00:42:46,335
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But why were Marina and Mitsuishi in it?</font>

594
00:42:46,435 --> 00:42:47,336
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There, there.</font>

595
00:42:47,403 --> 00:42:49,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You'll never be famous if you fuss
over such things.</font>

596
00:42:50,072 --> 00:42:51,374
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes! Let's all go.</font>

597
00:42:51,440 --> 00:42:52,308
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go!</font>

598
00:42:52,375 --> 00:42:53,809
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're coming too, right, Uehara?</font>

599
00:42:53,910 --> 00:42:54,744
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll pass.</font>

600
00:42:55,878 --> 00:42:56,946
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

601
00:42:57,446 --> 00:42:58,948
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Let's go.
-I said I'll pass.</font>

602
00:42:59,015 --> 00:43:00,616
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on. Everyone's going.</font>

603
00:43:00,683 --> 00:43:02,051
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Seriously?</font>

604
00:43:02,518 --> 00:43:03,586
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez.</font>

605
00:43:21,704 --> 00:43:24,273
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>The only one that can
make Marina smile is Mitsuishi,</i></font>

606
00:43:24,373 --> 00:43:27,109
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>and the only one that
can make Mitsuishi smile is Marina.</i></font>

607
00:43:28,444 --> 00:43:30,846
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara! We did it!</i></font>

608
00:43:32,582 --> 00:43:34,717
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Why don't you come, Uehara?
-I'm not part of it.</i></font>

609
00:43:34,817 --> 00:43:36,085
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>It's fine.</i></font>

610
00:43:43,893 --> 00:43:44,961
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

611
00:43:51,567 --> 00:43:52,802
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume.</font>

612
00:43:54,837 --> 00:43:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

613
00:43:58,074 --> 00:43:59,408
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I could ask you the same thing.</font>

614
00:43:59,542 --> 00:44:01,711
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara said he would come to the party</font>

615
00:44:01,811 --> 00:44:03,379
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but he disappeared.</font>

616
00:44:07,383 --> 00:44:08,384
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

617
00:44:08,451 --> 00:44:09,952
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You better get moving too, Natsume.</font>

618
00:44:10,019 --> 00:44:11,587
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everyone is headed to the place already.</font>

619
00:44:13,856 --> 00:44:14,757
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll pass.</font>

620
00:44:16,993 --> 00:44:18,861
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Group gatherings aren't really my thing.</font>

621
00:44:19,795 --> 00:44:21,530
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That excuse again.</font>

622
00:44:27,637 --> 00:44:30,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Natsume, thank you.</font>

623
00:44:36,712 --> 00:44:38,347
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You helped in so many ways.</font>

624
00:44:41,183 --> 00:44:42,285
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you so much.</font>

625
00:44:56,832 --> 00:44:58,234
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're welcome.</font>

626
00:45:12,515 --> 00:45:13,883
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's Uehara.</font>

627
00:45:32,168 --> 00:45:35,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She comes looking for me,
but she's the one who gets lost.</font>

628
00:45:46,682 --> 00:45:48,884
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Natsume...</font>

629
00:46:02,298 --> 00:46:03,632
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now I'm okay.</font>

630
00:46:08,604 --> 00:46:11,140
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was the prince, but I never
got to hold any women.</font>

631
00:46:11,707 --> 00:46:13,709
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I felt like something was unfinished
this whole time.</font>

632
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:19,682
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But now I'm satisfied.</font>

633
00:46:21,984 --> 00:46:23,886
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Have fun at the party.</font>

634
00:46:28,190 --> 00:46:30,192
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You really are too flirty!</font>

635
00:46:30,893 --> 00:46:31,927
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell?</font>

636
00:46:33,062 --> 00:46:34,263
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The worst...</font>

637
00:46:49,412 --> 00:46:50,813
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell am I doing?</font>

638
00:48:47,029 --> 00:48:50,399
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS DRAMA IS FICTIONAL.</font>

639
00:48:50,466 --> 00:48:52,468
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Subtitle translation by
Kumar Sivasubramanian</font>
